00:24:07.676 --> 00:24:09.166 A:middle
that are more design based.

00:24:10.256 --> 00:24:12.826 A:middle
And also the mentality
you need to keep in mind

00:24:13.396 --> 00:24:15.406 A:middle
for making great apps.

00:24:16.736 --> 00:24:18.856 A:middle
First of all, it's
the iconography.

00:24:19.716 --> 00:24:23.296 A:middle
Now you know that when you go to
the App Store and you're looking

00:24:23.296 --> 00:24:25.166 A:middle
for an app one of the
first things you're going

00:24:25.166 --> 00:24:26.456 A:middle
to notice is that icon.

00:24:27.006 --> 00:24:29.036 A:middle
And oftentimes, at
