00:24:36.446 --> 00:24:39.546 A:middle
So icons are really important,
and it's also important

00:24:39.546 --> 00:24:42.816 A:middle
that the icon that
you choose works well

00:24:43.186 --> 00:24:45.676 A:middle
for different languages
and also languages that go

00:24:45.676 --> 00:24:48.586 A:middle
in different layout directions

00:24:48.586 --> 00:24:49.976 A:middle
like left-to-right
or right-to-left.

00:24:50.576 --> 00:24:53.346 A:middle
So photos has a great icon here.

00:24:53.346 --> 00:24:58.036 A:middle
This is a great example of an
icon that doesn't have any words

00:24:58.036 --> 00:25:02.056 A:middle
or numbers that would tie
it to a specific language.

