00:25:04.406 --> 00:25:05.916 A:middle
like left-to-right
or right-to-left.

00:25:06.286 --> 00:25:08.966 A:middle
So it really works well,
you know, in Japanese,

00:25:08.966 --> 00:25:10.426 A:middle
in English, and in Arabic.

00:25:11.166 --> 00:25:15.886 A:middle
Now if you are making a
right-to-left localization,

00:25:16.326 --> 00:25:19.566 A:middle
and you want to make sure
your UI is really good

00:25:19.566 --> 00:25:20.706 A:middle
for right-to-left languages.

00:25:21.676 --> 00:25:23.856 A:middle
You should take a look at some
of the artwork you're using.

00:25:24.186 --> 00:25:27.146 A:middle
And if you are using artwork
that has a directionality to it

00:25:27.326 --> 00:25:29.686 A:middle
that would need to change
for a right-to-left language,

00:25:30.046 --> 00:25:33.916 A:middle
then you would probably need to
flip or create dedicated artwork

00:25:33.916 --> 00:25:35.106 A:middle
for right-to-left languages.

00:25:35.466 --> 00:25:38.116 A:middle
Now here you see an
example of artwork

00:25:38.116 --> 00:25:39.976 A:middle
that you can't just
