00:25:39.976 --> 00:25:42.306 A:middle
You need to create
dedicated artwork if you're

00:25:42.436 --> 00:25:43.656 A:middle
in a right-to-left language.

00:25:44.976 --> 00:25:47.776 A:middle
But if you do have images
that just need to be flipped,

00:25:47.846 --> 00:25:49.796 A:middle
there is actually API for
that and you don't need

00:25:49.796 --> 00:25:50.886 A:middle
to create separate artwork.

00:25:51.826 --> 00:25:54.376 A:middle
There's more information about
