00:26:03.876 --> 00:26:06.866 A:middle
Another thing that you might
or might not have thought

00:26:06.866 --> 00:26:08.476 A:middle
about is your app's name.

00:26:09.776 --> 00:26:12.896 A:middle
Now, when looking at various
App Stores around the world,

00:26:13.166 --> 00:26:16.036 A:middle
one consistent theme we've
seen that doesn't surprise us

00:26:16.036 --> 00:26:19.506 A:middle
in the least is that users
are more likely to buy apps

00:26:19.846 --> 00:26:21.656 A:middle
that work for them
in their language.

00:26:21.936 --> 00:26:24.356 A:middle
And that applies to
the apps' name as well.

00:26:24.916 --> 00:26:27.986 A:middle
Because if they can -- if they
can understand easily what your

00:26:27.986 --> 00:26:31.516 A:middle
app does by looking at the
one line name and description,

00:26:31.826 --> 00:26:33.776 A:middle
then they're much more likely

00:26:34.046 --> 00:26:40.426 A:middle
to tap inside the
app to take a look.

00:26:40.426 --> 00:26:42.966 A:middle
And of course, the world is --

00:26:43.516 --> 00:26:47.046 A:middle
users all over the world are
more and more multilingual

00:26:47.246 --> 00:26:48.866 A:middle
or at least they're bilingual.

00:26:49.426 --> 00:26:52.926 A:middle
So your app should
not make assumptions

00:26:53.016 --> 00:26:58.586 A:middle
about the UI language and
how it relates to the content

00:26:58.786 --> 00:26:59.776 A:middle
that the user will type.

00:27:00.256 --> 00:27:04.766 A:middle
For example, a very common theme
you will see all over countries

00:27:04.806 --> 00:27:08.196 A:middle
in Asia like India
and Southeast Asia is

00:27:08.196 --> 00:27:10.906 A:middle
that people will run
their phones in English,

00:27:11.326 --> 00:27:14.556 A:middle
but they'll have content
in their local languages

00:27:14.556 --> 00:27:15.786 A:middle
like Hindi in this case.

00:27:16.806 --> 00:27:20.996 A:middle
So when you have an app and you
run in English, don't assume

00:27:20.996 --> 00:27:22.706 A:middle
that the user's going
to type English text,

00:27:22.786 --> 00:27:25.896 A:middle
especially make sure to
test your app with Chinese

00:27:25.896 --> 00:27:27.416 A:middle
and Japanese keyboards
to make sure

00:27:27.416 --> 00:27:29.036 A:middle
that the experience works well.

