And here's an example that I
wanted to show you of an app

00:27:37.726 --> 00:27:40.886 A:middle
that in our opinion
does a really great job

00:27:40.886 --> 00:27:42.186 A:middle
at the things I just
talked about.

00:27:43.616 --> 00:27:44.516 A:middle
So this is Evernote.

00:27:45.286 --> 00:27:47.826 A:middle
And first of all,
you'll see the app icon.

00:27:48.546 --> 00:27:50.466 A:middle
It doesn't have any words
or symbols or anything

00:27:50.466 --> 00:27:53.446 A:middle
that would associate it
with a single language.

00:27:54.596 --> 00:27:55.826 A:middle
So that's great.

00:27:58.036 --> 00:27:59.976 A:middle
However, they have also gone

00:28:00.176 --> 00:28:03.496 A:middle
and localized their
app name into Chinese.

00:28:03.546 --> 00:28:05.536 A:middle
And this is actually if
you're a Chinese speaker,

00:28:05.536 --> 00:28:10.006 A:middle
you'll see that they have
a great visual pun in there

00:28:10.106 --> 00:28:12.066 A:middle
because the Chinese word

00:28:12.066 --> 00:28:15.336 A:middle
that they've chosen also
contains the character

00:28:15.336 --> 00:28:20.616 A:middle
for elephant, which is their
icons, which is kind of cool.

00:28:20.836 --> 00:28:23.336 A:middle
You'll also notice that they
have localized screenshots.

00:28:24.246 --> 00:28:29.366 A:middle
And there's a lot of attention
to detail in those screenshots.

00:28:29.366 --> 00:28:32.016 A:middle
You'll see, for example, that
in the localized screenshot

00:28:32.276 --> 00:28:34.726 A:middle
in which they're
creating a note,

00:28:35.516 --> 00:28:37.586 A:middle
you actually have the
Chinese keyboard on screen.

00:28:37.586 --> 00:28:39.116 A:middle
So the user is seeing

00:28:39.586 --> 00:28:42.336 A:middle
in the screenshots exactly the
experience that they're going

00:28:42.336 --> 00:28:43.756 A:middle
to get when they
download this app.

00:28:43.996 --> 00:28:45.806 A:middle
This is exactly what
users expect to see.

00:28:46.206 --> 00:28:47.416 A:middle
So take advantage of the fact

00:28:47.416 --> 00:28:50.506 A:middle
that you can upload
localized names, descriptions,

00:28:50.506 --> 00:28:54.516 A:middle
and screenshots to
the App Store.

00:28:55.026 --> 00:28:59.156 A:middle
And lastly, I wanted to talk
about surprise and delight.

00:28:59.296 --> 00:29:03.166 A:middle
What you can do to go above and
