using a specific language

00:29:07.396 --> 00:29:08.446 A:middle
or in a specific country.

00:29:09.856 --> 00:29:10.946 A:middle
I'll give a couple of examples.

00:29:11.376 --> 00:29:15.786 A:middle
One is if you have any
kind of predefined content

00:29:15.786 --> 00:29:18.966 A:middle
such as templates and pages.

00:29:20.196 --> 00:29:24.576 A:middle
You could create
different customized content

00:29:24.576 --> 00:29:25.616 A:middle
