00:30:05.156 --> 00:30:07.186 A:middle
Now what your app
does is really --

00:30:07.186 --> 00:30:09.236 A:middle
depends on what your app does.

00:30:09.706 --> 00:30:12.276 A:middle
And so you need to take a
look at your own app and see

00:30:12.276 --> 00:30:16.476 A:middle
